extends layout

block content
  h1  Jaybot7 Image Search Abstraction Layer
  h2 User Story: I can get the image URLs, alt text and page urls for a set of images relating to a given search string.
  p1  example input: thiswebpage.com/imagesearch/blue banana
  <BR><BR>
  p1  example output: '{"image url":"https://i.ytimg.com/vi/61cDTnfhAgo/maxresdefault.jpg","alt-text":"Blue Banana Stream","page url":"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=61cDTnfhAgo"}...'
      
  h2 User Story: I can paginate through the responses by adding a ?offset=2 parameter to the URL.
  p1    example input: thiswebpage.com/imagesearch/blue banana?offset=2
      
  h2 User Story: I can get a list of the most recently submitted search strings.
  p1    example input: thiswebpage.com/latest
  
  p1    example output: [{"terms":"blue banana","when":"2016-06-23T04:37:42.038Z"}...
